# LLM Model Catalog Edits (TS-21 / TS-23)

When editing [llm-model-catalog.json](../../config/llm-model-catalog.json), [adapter-preset-matrix.json](../../config/adapter-preset-matrix.json), or their JSON Schemas:

1. Keep catalog aligned with [TECH_STACK_LLM_MODEL_CATALOG.md](../../docs/decisions/TECH_STACK_LLM_MODEL_CATALOG.md) (TS-21 ADR)
2. User extensions (new models / adapter rows): follow [TECH_STACK_USER_EXTENSIBLE_LLM.md](../../docs/decisions/TECH_STACK_USER_EXTENSIBLE_LLM.md) (TS-23) — run `npm run validate:config` and `npm run test:contract`
3. Update [OPENAI_PROMPT_GUIDANCE.md](../../docs/OPENAI_PROMPT_GUIDANCE.md) when `prompting.*` fields change
4. Same commit: both READMEs if customer-facing model IDs or tiers change — see [documentation-sync.mdc](./documentation-sync.mdc)
5. Do not bypass Wall-Bounce constitution for routing/analysis changes affecting production behavior

